== EQUIPMENT
You have 2 wielded items, Interact to switch to a different set. 

/* Discuss: Armor reduces damage you take at Settle|end of turn, 1 for 1. */

=== 1-handed items (Wield any two.)

Shield
Raise shield. Reroll any number of damage dice on you OR clear one. 

Melee weapon
Attack. Deal 1d8i close to you. 
_Swords, spears, axes, and various other weapons wielded in one hand._

Off-hand weapon
Backhand attack. Deal 1d4i close to you. 

Implement
Blast. Deal 1d4i close or far from you. 
_Scepters, wands and similar item that can channel magical energy into a forceful blast or spells._

Wand of icy gusts
As wand, and mark stress to add Cold (up to 1). 

Standard
Rally. Mark Stress to grant all heroes advantage on a test of Mettle. Take this action when it is rolled, and it counts as your first one this round. 
_A banner or other ostentatious symbol, meant to strengthen resolve and serve as an impressive display._

Magical trinket
Focus. Reroll any number of damage dice you dealt with one spell this turn. 
_Often a spellbook, scroll, prayer wheel, religious symbol or other such magical aid._

=== 2-handed items (Wield only one.)

Heavy weapon
(Adv) Break something down, or open. 
Attack. Deal 1d12i close to you. 
_Greatclubs, longswords, greataxes and various other weapons that require both hands to strike._

Bow
Shoot. Deal 1d8i close or far from you. 

